==English==
===Etymology===
{{wikipedia}}
Possibly from Old English [[grëmian]], meaning, "to [[vex]]" or, "to [[anger]]", from [[grim]], "[[severe]]" , and related to German [[grämen]] and Swedish [[gräma]], "to grieve". 

