===Noun===
'''gremlin'''
#A [[mythical]] creature reputed to be mechanically inclined and [[mischievous]].
#By extension, any mysterious, unknown source of [[trouble]] or [[mischief]].
#:''We rechecked everything, and we suspect '''gremlins''' in the database.''
